{
  "name": "WF5 — Patient Reactivation (30-Day)",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Workflow 5: Patient Reactivation\n\n**Trigger:** Every Monday at 9:00 AM\n\n**Logic:** Finds patients who have been inactive for 30+ days (last message sent 30+ days ago or never messaged), haven't received a reactivation message yet, and are not already inactive/completed.\n\nSets `reactivation_sent = TRUE` after sending — ensures one-time delivery.\n\n**Before activating:**\n1. Set credential on all Google Sheets nodes → Google Sheets account\n2. Set credential on Send Reactivation node → Twilio Basic Auth\n\n**Note:** Meta category for this template is MARKETING — ensure opt-in compliance.",
        "height": 300,
        "width": 440
      },
      "id": "55555555-5555-5555-5555-000000000001",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [240, 60]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "cronExpression",
              "expression": "0 9 * * 1"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "55555555-5555-5555-5555-000000000002",
      "name": "Weekly Monday 9AM Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [240, 380]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "read",
        "documentId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "={{ $env.GOOGLE_SHEETS_ID }}",
          "mode": "id"
        },
        "sheetName": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "Patients",
          "mode": "name"
        },
        "filtersUI": {},
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "55555555-5555-5555-5555-000000000003",
      "name": "Read Patients",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [460, 380],
      "credentials": {
        "googleSheetsOAuth2Api": {
          "id": "REPLACE_WITH_GSHEETS_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "Google Sheets account"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Filter patients inactive for 30+ days who haven't been reactivated\nconst items = $input.all();\nconst tz = $env.TIMEZONE || 'Asia/Kolkata';\nconst inactivityDays = 30;\n\nconst now = new Date();\nconst thresholdDate = new Date(now);\nthresholdDate.setDate(thresholdDate.getDate() - inactivityDays);\n\nconst filtered = items.filter(item => {\n  const p = item.json;\n\n  // Must not already be inactive or completed\n  if (p.status === 'inactive' || p.status === 'completed') return false;\n\n  // Must not have already received reactivation message\n  const reactivationSent = p.reactivation_sent;\n  if (reactivationSent === true || reactivationSent === 'TRUE' || reactivationSent === '1') return false;\n\n  // Must have a valid phone number\n  if (!p.phone || !/^\\+[1-9]\\d{6,14}$/.test(p.phone.replace(/[\\s\\-().]/g, ''))) return false;\n\n  // Check inactivity: either never messaged, or last message > 30 days ago\n  if (p.last_message_sent) {\n    const lastSent = new Date(p.last_message_sent);\n    if (lastSent > thresholdDate) return false; // messaged within 30 days — skip\n  }\n  // If last_message_sent is blank, patient was never messaged — include them\n\n  return true;\n});\n\nif (filtered.length === 0) {\n  return [{ json: { _skip: true, reason: 'No inactive patients to reactivate this week' } }];\n}\n\nreturn filtered.map(item => ({\n  json: {\n    ...item.json,\n    _workflow: 'workflow-5-reactivation',\n    _message_type: 'reactivation',\n    _to_phone: 'whatsapp:' + item.json.phone.replace(/[\\s\\-().]/g, ''),\n    _message_body: `Hi ${item.json.name || 'there'}! 👋 It's been a while since we last saw you at ${item.json.clinic_name || ($env.DEFAULT_CLINIC_NAME || 'our clinic')}, and we just wanted to check in.\\n\\nRegular health check-ups with ${item.json.doctor_name || ($env.DEFAULT_DOCTOR_NAME || 'your doctor')} are the best way to stay ahead of any concerns. If you'd like to book an appointment, reply *BOOK* and our team will reach out.\\n\\nTake care! 💙`\n  }\n}));"
      },
      "id": "55555555-5555-5555-5555-000000000004",
      "name": "Filter Inactive Patients",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [680, 380]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": false,
            "leftValue": "",
            "typeValidation": "loose"
          },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "skip-check-wf5",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json._skip }}",
              "rightValue": true,
              "operator": {
                "type": "boolean",
                "operation": "true"
              }
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "55555555-5555-5555-5555-000000000005",
      "name": "Skip if No Patients",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [900, 380]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "={{ 'https://api.twilio.com/2010-04-01/Accounts/' + $env.TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID + '/Messages.json' }}",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "httpBasicAuth",
        "sendBody": true,
        "contentType": "form-urlencoded",
        "bodyParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "To",
              "value": "={{ $json._to_phone }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "From",
              "value": "={{ $env.TWILIO_WHATSAPP_NUMBER }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Body",
              "value": "={{ $json._message_body }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "retry": {
            "maxTries": 3,
            "waitBetweenTries": 30000
          }
        }
      },
      "id": "55555555-5555-5555-5555-000000000006",
      "name": "Send Reactivation Message",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [1120, 280],
      "credentials": {
        "httpBasicAuth": {
          "id": "REPLACE_WITH_TWILIO_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "Twilio Basic Auth"
        }
      },
      "onError": "continueErrorOutput"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "update",
        "documentId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "={{ $env.GOOGLE_SHEETS_ID }}",
          "mode": "id"
        },
        "sheetName": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "Patients",
          "mode": "name"
        },
        "columns": {
